title: War of the Roses: The Bathroom Hook-up
description: Matt met his current girlfriend Jenny while he was at a Happy Hour.  They hit it off and got right down to business in the bathroom of the bar that same day.  Matt likes her a lot but is nervous that Jenny might be cheating just because of the way they met.  Should Matt just trust her or nah?
